translation: He is unassailable, fearless, the Primal Entity and Boundless.
He is unassailable, invincible, Primal, non-dual and very difficult to realise.8.

gurmukhi: AnMq Awid dyv hY ] ibAMq Brm Byv hY ]
transliteration: Anant Aadh Dev Hai|| Biant Bharam Bhev Hai||
translation: He is Boundless and Primal Lord; He is endless and Indiscriminate from illusion.

gurmukhi: AgwiD ibAwiD nws hY ] sdYv srb pws hY ]1]9]
transliteration: Agaddh(i) Biaadh(i) Naas Hai|| Sadaiv Sarab Paas Hai||1||9||
translation: He is Unfathomable and Destroyer of ailments; He is always with everyone.1.9.

gurmukhi: bicqR icqR cwD hYN ] AKMf duSt Kwp hYN ]
transliteration: Bachitra Chitra Chaap Hain|| Akhanndddousht Khaap Hain||
translation: His painting is marvelous; He is Indivisible and Destroyer on tyrants.

gurmukhi: AByd Awid kwl hYN ] sdYv srb pwl hYN ]2]10]
transliteration: Abhed Aadh Kaal Hain|| Sadaiv Sarab Paal Hain||2||10||
translation: He is Indiscriminate from the very beginning and always sustains all.2.10.

gurmukhi: AKMf cMf rUp hYN ] pRcMf srb srUp hYN ]
transliteration: Akhannddchannd Roop Hain|| Prachanndd Sarab Saroophain||
translation: He is Indivisible and hast terrible form; His Powerful Entity manifests all.

gurmukhi: kwl hUM ky kwl hYN ] sdYv r`C pwl hYN ]3]11]
transliteration: Kaal Hoon Ke Kaal Hain|| Sadaiv Rachh Paal Hain||3||11||
translation: He is the death of death and is also always the Protector.3.11.

gurmukhi: kiRpwl idAwl rUp hYN ] sdYv srb BUp hYN ]
transliteration: Kridaal Diaal Roop Hain|| Sadaiv Sarab Bhoop Hain||
translation: He is the Kind and Merciful entity and is ever the Sovereign of all.

gurmukhi: AnMq srb Aws hYN ] pryv prm pws hYN ]4]12]
transliteration: Anant Sarab Aas Hain|| Darev Param Paas Hain||4||12||
translation: He is boundless and fulfiller of the hopes of all; He is very far away and also very near.4.12.

gurmukhi: AdiRst AMqr iDAwn hYN ] sdYv srb mwn hYN ]
transliteration: Adrist Antar Dhiaan Hain|| Sadaiv Sarab Maan Hain||
translation: He is Invisible but abides in inner meditation; He is always honoured by all.

gurmukhi: kiRpwl kwl hIn hYN ] sdYv swD ADIn hYN ]5]13]
transliteration: Kridaal Kaal Heen Hain|| Sadaiv Saadh Adheen Hain||5||13||
translation: He is Merciful and Eternal and is always honoured by all.5.13.
Therefore I meditate on Thee, I meditate on Thee.PUSE.
